What you need to know:  Affectionately known as Khadra, the signer was born in Hargeisa in 1957 when the region was still a colony.Many playwrights wanted Khadra included in their shows. She performed in such theatrical shows as “Dab Jacayl Kariwaa” by Hassan Ganeey.On record is that Khadra had over 250 chart-hitting songs.